  m_Name: No.2
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  OrderIdx: 2
  Title: "GI\xC1 TR\u1ECA C\u1ED0T L\xD5I "
  HexCode: 0xEE
  Content:
  - "Trong m\u1ED9t th\u1EBF gi\u1EDBi c\xF4ng ngh\u1EC7 thay \u0111\u1ED5i li\xEAn
    t\u1EE5c, UIT kh\xF4ng mu\u1ED1n sinh vi\xEAn ch\u1EC9 h\u1ECDc c\xE1ch l\xE0m
    theo nh\u1EEFng g\xEC \u0111\xE3 c\xF3.\\n Tinh th\u1EA7n d\xE1m th\u1EED, d\xE1m
    \u0111\u1ED5i m\u1EDBi v\xE0 lu\xF4n t\xECm ra h\u01B0\u1EDBng \u0111i kh\xE1c
    bi\u1EC7t ch\xEDnh l\xE0 gi\xE1 tr\u1ECB ________ m\xE0 nh\xE0 tr\u01B0\u1EDDng
    lu\xF4n theo \u0111u\u1ED5i."
  - "Nh\xE0 tr\u01B0\u1EDDng h\u01B0\u1EDBng t\u1EDBi vi\u1EC7c \u0111\xE0o t\u1EA1o
    sinh vi\xEAn kh\xF4ng ch\u1EC9 m\u1EA1nh v\u1EC1 chuy\xEAn m\xF4n m\xE0 c\xF2n
    c\xF3 t\u01B0 duy ph\u1EA3n bi\u1EC7n, k\u1EF9 n\u0103ng m\u1EC1m v\xE0 tr\xE1ch
    nhi\u1EC7m x\xE3 h\u1ED9i. \\n \u0110\xF3 l\xE0 tri\u1EBFt l\xFD ph\xE1t tri\u1EC3n
    con ng\u01B0\u1EDDi m\u1ED9t c\xE1ch ________"
  - "UIT tin r\u1EB1ng tri th\u1EE9c ch\u1EC9 th\u1EF1c s\u1EF1 c\xF3 \xFD ngh\u0129a
    khi \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c d\xF9ng \u0111\u1EC3 t\u1EA1o ra gi\xE1 tr\u1ECB cho
    c\u1ED9ng \u0111\u1ED3ng. V\xEC th\u1EBF, \u201C________ x\xE3 h\u1ED9i\u201D
    tr\u1EDF th\xE0nh m\u1ED9t trong ba tri\u1EBFt l\xFD \u0111\xE0o t\u1EA1o c\u1ED1t
    l\xF5i c\u1EE7a nh\xE0 tr\u01B0\u1EDDng su\u1ED1t nhi\u1EC1u n\u0103m qua. "
  Keys:
  - key: 2
    value: SANGTAO
  - key: 3
    value: TOANDIEN
  - key: 8
    value: PHUNGSU
